# Managed git — backend that NEW managed repos provision on (provider-agnostic
# registry; github is the default + only active backend). These are server-side
# creds ONLY — the sandbox never sees them; it talks to the Kortix git proxy via
# KORTIX_TOKEN. MANAGED_GIT_GITHUB_TOKEN is a managed-org PAT (takes precedence
# when set); _INSTALL_ID is the GitHub App fallback. isConfigured() needs OWNER
